<section class="bg-gray-950">
  <div class="md:max-w-4xl md:mx-auto">
    <%= render "layouts/flash" %>
  </div>

  <div class="md:max-w-4xl md:mx-auto md:flex md:flex-row py-8">
    <div class="md:w-[50%] text-left md:flex md:flex-col md:gap-4 mx-6 lg:mx-0 my-8">
      <h1 class="md:text-7xl text-6xl font-bold text-white">
        Vote for the&nbsp;Student Council
      </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-[50%] content-end mx-6 md:mx-0 md:gap-4 my-8">
      <%= link_to vote_url do %>
        <button class="mx-auto bg-blue-600 p-4 rounded-md my-6 md:my-0 text-white font-bold mr-4 lg:mr-0">
          VOTE NOW
        </button>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="">
  <div class="md:max-w-4xl md:mx-auto md:py-24 py-12 mx-6">
    <div class="md:flex md:flex-row flex flex-col md:gap-16 gap-6">
      <div class="md:w-[50%] flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Why vote?</h3>
          <p class="mb-2">
            The Student Council is an independent, elected and self-organised body
            whose goal is to enhance student experience. It will take care of
            various issues, ensure clarity of communication between student body
            and the staff, will listen to students and voice their wishes and
            concerns in a proactive, result-oriented manner. This way students
            can focus on their study and life at Codam.
          </p>
          <p>
            The Student Council represents you and works to address your concerns.
            By participating in the elections, you get to choose the individuals
            who will directly advocate for you, communicate with you, and
            collaborate with the staff to make positive changes.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Unsure how to cast your vote?</h3>
          <p class="mb-2">
            Check out the motivation of our candidates and don't hesitate to
            reach out to us, either in person or on Slack.
          </p>
          <p>
            Join the Open stage with the candidates. Come to have a chat, ask
            any questions regarding the council or voice your wishes and concerns.<br>
            <span class="font-bold">Thursday 20/03, 14:00, Game room.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-[50%]">
        <div class="">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">How do I vote?</h3>
          <ul class="ml-4 list-disc flex flex-col gap-2">
            <li>Voting is open from 17/03 to 23/03.</li>
            <li>
              Follow the <%= link_to "vote", vote_url, class: "text-blue-500 hover:underline" %>
              link to view the candidates and cast your vote.
            </li>
            <li>Every vote is anonymous.</li>
            <li>You can only vote once.</li>
            <li>Your vote is final and cannot be changed.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
